                    "message": {
                        "text": "Math.mulDiv(uint256,uint256,uint256) (../sb/Cartorio_F.sol#2527-2598) has bitwise-xor operator ^ instead of the exponentiation operator **: \n\t - inverse = (3 * denominator) ^ 2 (../sb/Cartorio_F.sol#2580)\n"
                    },
                    "ruleId": "slither_0_11_3_incorrect_exp"
