                        "text": "Math.mulDiv(uint256,uint256,uint256) (../sb/Cartorio_F.sol#2527-2598) performs a multiplication on the result of a division:\n\t- denominator = denominator / twos (../sb/Cartorio_F.sol#2565)\n\t- inverse *= 2 - denominator * inverse (../sb/Cartorio_F.sol#2587)\n"
